  {
    "client_msg_id": "362f6eac-5c09-432e-95e4-c9d2505ca99c",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I also would like to have one-on-one chat.\n\nI also not working on anything particular now, but I'm generally interested in moving programming away from text-basing languages to structure based programs. If we develop this idea about structured programs and what kind of properties they gonna have, it gets really interesting.\n\nI sketch some ideas here and there.",
